name: e9Art - every day is mummys day ...

metadata.name: mummy knows everything
metadata.description:
every day is mummy's day ...

the thing i like best about using AI as a creative tool is the unexpected results i get back when i type in my text prompt ...

and in this case, what happens when i make a couple of typos ! 

such happy little accidents ...

which, in turn, give me exactly the things i desire most in my life: 

childlike wonder, joyful surprise and playful adventure.

digital art by e9Art using disco diffusion and photoshop, April 2022
